<div align="center">
<sub>001 — IDENTITY</sub>
</div>

<h2 align="center">Not a résumé. A working record.</h2>

<p align="center" width="600">
I build software end-to-end — Android apps, web platforms, and the AI tooling in between.<br/>
Based in Bangladesh. Self-taught. No formal CS background — just several years<br/>
of shipping things, breaking them, and shipping them better.
</p>

