<div align="center">
<sub>002 — MISSION</sub>
</div>

<h2 align="center">Software should disappear into the experience.</h2>

<p align="center" width="600">
I don't design for demos. I design for the person who opens the app at 2am<br/>
because something needs to work, right now. That's the bar — not "impressive,"<br/>
just <i>correct, fast, and honest</i> about what it does.
</p>

